snippet.title: Ascendum - Early Trailer
snippet.description:
Official Trailer for Ascendum, the first official game made by Team Caecus
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1504090/Ascendum/
---------------------------------------------------------
Help 2 twin vessels to ascend on the top of the mysterious golden mountain! Overcome platforming and mind-bending puzzle challenges, and defeat scary enemies and bosses while controlling both characters at the same time or working together with another player in local Co-op.

Check out other team members:
Lukianze
- Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/user-864799849-361065325 
- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/lukianze/

Nico
- https://www.youtube.com/channel/UClcGpefuIXCELDoYa5lIlOw
